data.description: Welcome to Independence at Mather! A quiet, well-kept community nestled away from the hustle and bustle. Situated on a corner lot with no back neighbors offering privacy and tranquility. This house boasts vaulted ceilings in the grand entry way, a living/dining room combination with window lined walls for ample natural light. The kitchen/nook/family room area is perfect for entertaining. The kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and pantry closet. Downstairs bedroom and full bathroom is perfect for guests or elderly family. Upstairs boasts an open loft with vaulted ceilings; master bedroom en-suite with two closets; hall bedroom and bathroom; a mini-master bedroom with en suite bathroom; and huge bonus room that can be used as 5th bedroom. Backyard has covered patio and cemented side which can be used for RV storage. Walking distance from elementary school; park with walking trail; and bike trails. Near shopping and coming-soon retail & Mather Golf Course.
